text: David Julian Dobrik (; born 23 July 1996) is a Slovakian-American YouTuber, podcaster, and co-founder of the photography app Dispo. He becames well known for his videos on Vine. He started his vlog on his YouTube channel in 2015. Dobrik was born in Ko≈°ice, Slovakia. His family moved to Illinois, United States when he was six years old and studied at Vernon Hills High School, where he played tennis. After graduating high school, he moved to Los Angeles to make videos on Vine.
